1
00:00:35,970 --> 00:00:38,890
= Angels and Guards=

2
00:00:38,890 --> 00:00:41,180
=Episode 2=

3
00:00:44,083 --> 00:00:45,791
You really are stubborn.

4
00:00:46,208 --> 00:00:47,916
So tell me. What do you want?

5
00:00:50,041 --> 00:00:51,333
You want to stay here

6
00:00:51,875 --> 00:00:53,458
and keep working at Northern Bureau?

7
00:00:54,375 --> 00:00:55,333
Then sell yourselves to me.

8
00:00:56,250 --> 00:00:56,833
For six months,

9
00:00:57,333 --> 00:00:58,500
you'll wait tables for free

10
00:00:58,500 --> 00:01:00,500
and do whatever I say.

11
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,166
Then I may consider

12
00:01:03,666 --> 00:01:05,250
wiping out all your debts.

13
00:01:05,916 --> 00:01:07,166
And I'll forget about

14
00:01:07,166 --> 00:01:09,083
you blasting me into my signboard.

15
00:01:18,625 --> 00:01:19,041
Fine.

16
00:01:19,833 --> 00:01:20,625
Then it's settled.

17
00:01:21,708 --> 00:01:23,750
But I now serve Northern Bureau,

18
00:01:23,750 --> 00:01:25,625
so I'm only yours in my spare time.

19
00:01:27,125 --> 00:01:27,875
Deal.

20
00:01:28,850 --> 00:01:31,930
(Chong'er Pavilion)

21
00:01:32,708 --> 00:01:33,250
All sliced.

22
00:01:33,250 --> 00:01:33,750
Take them out.

23
00:01:33,916 --> 00:01:34,583
Okay.

24
00:01:35,291 --> 00:01:36,166
Set that here for now.

25
00:01:36,166 --> 00:01:37,500
Hua has it easy.

26
00:01:37,666 --> 00:01:38,791
She serves guests in private rooms,

27
00:01:38,791 --> 00:01:40,000
with all the good food and wine.

28
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,541
And we're stuck doing grunt work.

29
00:01:41,791 --> 00:01:44,250
But at least
we got into Chong'er Pavilion.

30
00:01:45,666 --> 00:01:47,416
Chang Beiming is crazy.

31
00:01:47,416 --> 00:01:48,666
We'd better watch our backs.

32
00:01:49,375 --> 00:01:51,833
Really? I think he's quite handsome.

33
00:01:52,791 --> 00:01:54,208
He made us sign our lives away,

34
00:01:54,541 --> 00:01:55,416
and you're defending him?

35
00:01:56,583 --> 00:01:57,458
Bingfan,

36
00:01:57,458 --> 00:01:59,208
we're already here.

37
00:01:59,750 --> 00:02:00,791
We might as well
look on the bright side.

38
00:02:01,125 --> 00:02:03,791
Mr. Chang is handsome and rich.

39
00:02:04,583 --> 00:02:05,375
I don't think working for him

40
00:02:05,375 --> 00:02:06,666
is such a bad deal.

41
00:02:08,541 --> 00:02:09,416
What do you mean by handsome?

42
00:02:13,208 --> 00:02:15,375
Handsome means...

43
00:02:16,041 --> 00:02:17,500
He's good-looking.

44
00:02:17,875 --> 00:02:19,000
His features are all in the right place.

45
00:02:19,833 --> 00:02:21,958
And every time I see him,

46
00:02:22,416 --> 00:02:24,041
I feel a little

47
00:02:24,625 --> 00:02:25,708
shy.

48
00:02:25,916 --> 00:02:27,375
I don't think he's handsome at all.

49
00:02:27,916 --> 00:02:29,000
Whenever I see him,

50
00:02:29,250 --> 00:02:30,416
my chest gets tight,

51
00:02:30,416 --> 00:02:31,208
and I want to hit someone.

52
00:02:32,208 --> 00:02:32,958
Bingfan,

53
00:02:34,041 --> 00:02:35,708
you're actually pretty handsome too.

54
00:02:36,416 --> 00:02:37,750
Even more than him.

55
00:02:41,458 --> 00:02:42,208
Miss Shen.

56
00:02:42,791 --> 00:02:45,125
(Chang Huan, attendant)
Mr. Chang wants you to clean his study.

57
00:02:45,291 --> 00:02:46,250
What?

58
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:08,810
(Guide to Joining the Jinyiwei)

59
00:03:09,083 --> 00:03:11,500
This is the Northern Bureau
onboarding guide.

60
00:03:12,541 --> 00:03:14,250
You can't buy this anywhere.

61
00:03:15,208 --> 00:03:16,166
Then how do you have it?

62
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:18,208
Because I took
the Northern Bureau exam too.

63
00:03:18,583 --> 00:03:19,125
Why?

64
00:03:19,625 --> 00:03:20,541
Because...

65
00:03:23,125 --> 00:03:25,250
Jinyiwei's Robe and Blade

66
00:03:26,083 --> 00:03:27,291
look amazing.

67
00:03:29,458 --> 00:03:30,166
Did you pass?

68
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,708
No.

69
00:03:33,583 --> 00:03:34,791
I ranked first in the written exam

70
00:03:36,041 --> 00:03:37,125
but failed the physical test.

71
00:03:38,416 --> 00:03:39,416
A grown man,

72
00:03:39,666 --> 00:03:41,208
and you couldn't pass the physical?

73
00:03:41,583 --> 00:03:42,458
And you admit that out loud?

74
00:03:44,375 --> 00:03:46,291
What gets you by these days?

75
00:03:46,583 --> 00:03:48,166
Brains.

76
00:03:49,958 --> 00:03:50,666
Come on.

77
00:03:50,666 --> 00:03:51,458
Start cleaning.

78
00:03:53,541 --> 00:03:54,916
From now on,

79
00:03:54,916 --> 00:03:56,333
we're landlord and tenant.

80
00:03:57,041 --> 00:03:58,000
We should look out for each other.

81
00:04:00,791 --> 00:04:01,625
Now, clean.

82
00:04:09,500 --> 00:04:10,125
Bingfan,

83
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,125
Hua told me everything.

84
00:04:12,125 --> 00:04:14,208
You're the famous

85
00:04:14,500 --> 00:04:15,250
female bounty hunter.

86
00:04:16,041 --> 00:04:17,791
I've always been a huge fan.

87
00:04:18,416 --> 00:04:19,833
You're my biggest hero.

88
00:04:20,166 --> 00:04:20,791
Well, and one other person.

89
00:04:21,708 --> 00:04:22,958
The phantom thief, Feng Fuliu.

90
00:04:23,750 --> 00:04:25,625
Feng Fuliu ranks second
on the bounty list,

91
00:04:25,625 --> 00:04:26,500
a Class-A fugitive.

92
00:04:26,750 --> 00:04:28,666
You can't idolize a wanted criminal.

93
00:04:30,333 --> 00:04:31,583
But he's so handsome.

94
00:04:34,666 --> 00:04:35,333
Let me do it, Xintian.

95
00:04:35,708 --> 00:04:36,291
Take a break.

96
00:04:37,333 --> 00:04:38,291
You shouldn't do this.

97
00:04:38,791 --> 00:04:39,500
Sit down.

98
00:04:41,208 --> 00:04:41,666
Sit.

99
00:04:43,291 --> 00:04:44,916
I brought these oranges from home.

100
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:45,708
Try one.

101
00:04:46,208 --> 00:04:47,041
The oranges back home

102
00:04:47,041 --> 00:04:47,708
are really sweet.

103
00:04:49,083 --> 00:04:49,625
Thank you.

104
00:04:51,458 --> 00:04:52,208
Bingfan.

105
00:04:52,916 --> 00:04:55,125
I've always wanted to thank you.

106
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:58,041
From now on, I'll do all the hard work.

107
00:04:58,041 --> 00:04:58,916
You don't have to worry about it.

108
00:04:59,583 --> 00:05:00,500
I can handle it all.

109
00:05:02,541 --> 00:05:05,125
I've always felt useless.

110
00:05:05,875 --> 00:05:08,500
My parents disliked me
since I was little.

111
00:05:08,916 --> 00:05:09,916
They thought I was stupid.

112
00:05:10,166 --> 00:05:11,333
So I always thought

113
00:05:11,958 --> 00:05:14,208
I shouldn't have been born.

114
00:05:18,750 --> 00:05:19,791
But you're different.

115
00:05:20,375 --> 00:05:21,791
You mean something to me.

116
00:05:22,625 --> 00:05:23,666
When I first met you,

117
00:05:24,041 --> 00:05:25,500
we didn't even know each other.

118
00:05:25,958 --> 00:05:27,041
But for my sake,

119
00:05:27,541 --> 00:05:29,083
you stood up to those men.

120
00:05:29,458 --> 00:05:30,250
Because of you,

121
00:05:30,916 --> 00:05:32,625
I get to live in a place this nice.

122
00:05:33,708 --> 00:05:34,333
Otherwise,

123
00:05:35,666 --> 00:05:37,291
I'd have to marry that old eunuch.

124
00:05:39,458 --> 00:05:40,583
If I hadn't met you,

125
00:05:41,833 --> 00:05:42,833
I honestly don't know

126
00:05:43,500 --> 00:05:44,875
how I would have gone on.

127
00:05:49,375 --> 00:05:50,083
So,

128
00:05:51,000 --> 00:05:51,583
Bingfan,

129
00:05:52,208 --> 00:05:54,291
let me follow you
for the rest of my life

130
00:05:54,583 --> 00:05:56,583
and be your little fangirl, okay?

131
00:06:06,791 --> 00:06:07,375
Okay.

132
00:06:08,583 --> 00:06:10,250
Then I'll take you as my little sister.

133
00:06:11,666 --> 00:06:14,041
Join me to register
at the Bureau tomorrow.

134
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:17,250
You mean, the Northern Bureau?

135
00:06:18,625 --> 00:06:19,416
Bingfan.

136
00:06:19,833 --> 00:06:21,750
I get to work for the court with you?

137
00:06:25,291 --> 00:06:26,583
Thank you so much, Bingfan.

138
00:06:44,125 --> 00:06:45,375
Northern Bureau,

139
00:06:46,333 --> 00:06:47,416
here I come.

140
00:06:48,310 --> 00:06:51,333
(Northern Bureau)

141
00:06:51,333 --> 00:06:52,416
It's beautiful.

142
00:07:02,333 --> 00:07:03,083
The real test

143
00:07:03,666 --> 00:07:05,666
will be set by the Commander himself.

144
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,333
For young women like you,

145
00:07:08,750 --> 00:07:09,958
to have such loyal hearts,

146
00:07:09,958 --> 00:07:11,791
devoted to the throne and the realm,

147
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,500
I am deeply pleased.

148
00:07:14,625 --> 00:07:16,250
Deeply pleased indeed.

149
00:07:17,166 --> 00:07:17,666
Therefore,

150
00:07:17,666 --> 00:07:20,958
I have decided
to waive the written exam.

151
00:07:21,333 --> 00:07:22,125
Go straight to the combat test.

152
00:07:22,333 --> 00:07:22,625
My lord!

153
00:07:22,625 --> 00:07:23,750
My mind is made up.

154
00:07:23,750 --> 00:07:24,541
No written exam?

155
00:07:24,541 --> 00:07:25,666
Unbelievable.

156
00:07:26,291 --> 00:07:27,250
Hua Mange will go first.

157
00:07:39,333 --> 00:07:40,000
Begin.

158
00:07:58,583 --> 00:07:59,458
Time's up.

159
00:08:00,541 --> 00:08:01,708
How did the incense burn so fast?

160
00:08:02,041 --> 00:08:02,791
We barely started.

161
00:08:02,791 --> 00:08:04,666
Right. How did it burn that quickly?

162
00:08:05,666 --> 00:08:06,625
It's already over?

163
00:08:10,958 --> 00:08:12,416
I can't do this. Maybe...

164
00:08:12,833 --> 00:08:14,083
Maybe I should just go home.

165
00:08:14,458 --> 00:08:15,166
I'm leaving.

166
00:08:16,666 --> 00:08:17,250
How about this?

167
00:08:17,500 --> 00:08:18,208
When it's your turn,

168
00:08:18,416 --> 00:08:19,125
you...

169
00:08:20,333 --> 00:08:20,916
Next.

170
00:08:21,166 --> 00:08:23,375
You. Xintian. Step forward.

171
00:08:55,291 --> 00:08:55,958
Wait.

172
00:08:58,208 --> 00:09:00,666
Sir, I'm just a weak young woman.

173
00:09:01,041 --> 00:09:02,125
I really can't beat you.

174
00:09:02,791 --> 00:09:04,625
Can we keep this friendly?

175
00:09:04,916 --> 00:09:07,166
Very well. I'll allow you three strikes.

176
00:09:10,291 --> 00:09:12,291
Sorry about this, sir.

177
00:09:38,875 --> 00:09:39,375
Time's up.

178
00:09:43,958 --> 00:09:44,291
What?

179
00:09:44,750 --> 00:09:46,958
She won!

180
00:09:49,041 --> 00:09:50,750
Bingfan. Mange.

181
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,416
My lord.

182
00:09:54,666 --> 00:09:55,125
This...

183
00:09:55,291 --> 00:09:56,125
This is cheating.

184
00:09:56,125 --> 00:09:56,875
My lord.

185
00:09:57,458 --> 00:09:59,250
Cheng Xintian

186
00:09:59,708 --> 00:10:02,041
stalled him on purpose.

187
00:10:02,041 --> 00:10:03,875
Then had someone land a cheap shot.

188
00:10:04,750 --> 00:10:05,250
Am I wrong?

189
00:10:05,250 --> 00:10:05,666
My lord,

190
00:10:06,458 --> 00:10:07,833
that is against the rules.

191
00:10:08,708 --> 00:10:09,416
Guokai,

192
00:10:09,708 --> 00:10:11,458
rules are made by people.

193
00:10:12,208 --> 00:10:13,708
No need to be so rigid.

194
00:10:15,666 --> 00:10:17,416
You said it, my lord.

195
00:10:18,541 --> 00:10:18,958
Cool.

196
00:10:19,250 --> 00:10:20,291
What do you mean?

197
00:10:20,458 --> 00:10:20,750
You.

198
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,541
Last one.

199
00:10:21,875 --> 00:10:22,583
Shen Bingfan, step forward.

200
00:10:29,916 --> 00:10:30,625
Zuo Da. Jiang Biao.

201
00:10:30,770 --> 00:10:31,373
(Zuo Da, Qianhu,
Northern Bureau's Captain)

202
00:10:31,375 --> 00:10:31,708
Yes.

203
00:10:31,791 --> 00:10:32,583
(Jiang Biao, Qianhu)
Yes.

204
00:10:36,791 --> 00:10:37,375
Two men?

205
00:10:37,666 --> 00:10:38,416
Us?

206
00:10:38,875 --> 00:10:39,333
That's right.

207
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:40,875
Two?.

208
00:10:43,083 --> 00:10:44,625
Against one woman,

209
00:10:45,083 --> 00:10:48,083
do you really need two of your best men?

210
00:10:48,083 --> 00:10:49,375
This lady warrior is known as

211
00:10:49,375 --> 00:10:51,250
the realm's greatest bounty hunter.

212
00:10:51,416 --> 00:10:53,083
I had to find two top Jinyiwei men

213
00:10:53,416 --> 00:10:54,416
to test her properly.

214
00:11:00,041 --> 00:11:00,541
Move.

215
00:11:07,916 --> 00:11:08,541
Begin.

216
00:11:26,375 --> 00:11:28,041
Come on!

217
00:11:28,416 --> 00:11:29,000
Fight!

218
00:11:29,416 --> 00:11:30,250
Get up!

219
00:11:32,458 --> 00:11:33,375
Get up!

220
00:11:33,500 --> 00:11:35,041
Up! Get up!

221
00:11:36,166 --> 00:11:36,666
Stop!

222
00:11:37,458 --> 00:11:38,416
You two useless fools.

223
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:39,208
Stand down!

224
00:11:40,166 --> 00:11:40,708
Come back.

225
00:11:47,875 --> 00:11:49,375
Bingfan, you're amazing!

226
00:11:52,791 --> 00:11:53,458
Useless.

227
00:11:58,333 --> 00:11:59,333
Duoyu,

228
00:11:59,416 --> 00:12:01,208
where are you taking us?

229
00:12:01,375 --> 00:12:01,958
The Records Office.

230
00:12:02,166 --> 00:12:03,458
You need an identity check,

231
00:12:03,708 --> 00:12:04,666
and then you'll be entered in the registry.

232
00:12:05,791 --> 00:12:07,958
Didn't we register yesterday?

233
00:12:08,541 --> 00:12:09,333
That was different.

234
00:12:09,541 --> 00:12:11,000
That was just the application.

235
00:12:11,208 --> 00:12:12,083
There's still the background check.

236
00:12:12,208 --> 00:12:13,291
Only after you pass

237
00:12:13,833 --> 00:12:15,083
can you become official Jinyiwei.

238
00:12:15,083 --> 00:12:15,666
May I ask

239
00:12:15,916 --> 00:12:17,375
which officer handles the check?

240
00:12:20,875 --> 00:12:21,500
Name.

241
00:12:21,958 --> 00:12:23,208
Hua Mange.

242
00:12:26,708 --> 00:12:28,222
(Hua Mange)

243
00:12:28,333 --> 00:12:29,041
Age.

244
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:30,500
Seventeen.

245
00:12:31,166 --> 00:12:32,041
Where are you from?

246
00:12:32,500 --> 00:12:33,083
Huguang.

247
00:12:34,208 --> 00:12:34,708
That's it?

248
00:12:35,541 --> 00:12:36,041
Yes.

249
00:12:36,208 --> 00:12:36,708
What?

250
00:12:36,958 --> 00:12:37,333
Then,

251
00:12:37,916 --> 00:12:39,250
what are your parents' names?

252
00:12:39,375 --> 00:12:40,166
Who trained you?

253
00:12:40,958 --> 00:12:42,958
I cannot reveal my parents' names.

254
00:12:43,791 --> 00:12:44,708
And my school

255
00:12:45,750 --> 00:12:46,416
must remain secret.

256
00:12:47,458 --> 00:12:47,916
What?

257
00:12:52,166 --> 00:12:52,541
My lord.

258
00:12:52,958 --> 00:12:54,416
What shall we do with the three women?

259
00:12:57,625 --> 00:12:58,541
What do you think?

260
00:12:58,541 --> 00:13:00,583
Hua Mange's origins are suspicious,

261
00:13:00,583 --> 00:13:01,250
but she can be admitted.

262
00:13:01,666 --> 00:13:02,291
Hua Mange.

263
00:13:02,291 --> 00:13:03,083
Background check passed.

264
00:13:03,708 --> 00:13:04,375
Enter her name.

265
00:13:04,750 --> 00:13:05,458
Cheng Xintian

266
00:13:05,458 --> 00:13:06,416
has a clean background.

267
00:13:06,416 --> 00:13:07,000
She can be admitted.

268
00:13:07,458 --> 00:13:07,958
Cheng Xintian.

269
00:13:07,958 --> 00:13:10,208
Background check passed. Enter her name.

270
00:13:12,083 --> 00:13:12,666
Only

271
00:13:12,666 --> 00:13:13,666
Shen Bingfan

272
00:13:13,666 --> 00:13:15,458
refuses to name her parents or school.

273
00:13:16,500 --> 00:13:17,416
This is really suspicious.

274
00:13:17,750 --> 00:13:18,416
Indeed.

275
00:13:19,625 --> 00:13:20,708
It is suspicious.

276
00:13:20,708 --> 00:13:22,625
Shen Bingfan's origins are unclear.

277
00:13:23,166 --> 00:13:23,958
She is rejected.

278
00:13:24,083 --> 00:13:24,833
Commissioner!

279
00:13:26,208 --> 00:13:27,375
Why the panic?

280
00:13:27,416 --> 00:13:28,541
Young Master Chang
of Chong'er Pavilion is here.

281
00:13:48,083 --> 00:13:49,000
Are you accepting me or not?

282
00:13:49,166 --> 00:13:51,416
Shen Bingfan's origins are unclear.

283
00:13:51,541 --> 00:13:52,416
She is rejected.

284
00:13:52,416 --> 00:13:54,958
Accepted. Accepted!

285
00:13:55,833 --> 00:13:57,083
Accepted. Accepted!

286
00:13:58,041 --> 00:14:00,000
Shen Bingfan. Background check passed.

287
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,500
Enter her name.

288
00:14:01,666 --> 00:14:02,125
My lord.

289
00:14:02,416 --> 00:14:02,791
My lord.

290
00:14:02,791 --> 00:14:03,541
Shut up!

291
00:14:04,416 --> 00:14:05,250
Enter her name. Now.

292
00:14:06,000 --> 00:14:06,458
Yes, my lord.

293
00:14:28,180 --> 00:14:31,350
♪Because you once entered my dreams♪

294
00:14:31,720 --> 00:14:35,100
♪Truth and illusion blur in wine♪

295
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:38,350
♪My heart drifted lost♪

296
00:14:38,350 --> 00:14:41,760
♪Yet found you in the crowd♪

297
00:14:42,850 --> 00:14:46,060
♪My blood still burns
as the world surges♪

298
00:14:46,470 --> 00:14:49,810
♪The land is fair, and you are free♪

299
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:52,600
♪Sword drawn, lost in obsession♪

300
00:14:52,600 --> 00:14:56,640
♪I've softly let it go♪

301
00:14:56,640 --> 00:15:00,510
♪The vow you made was true♪

302
00:15:00,510 --> 00:15:04,260
♪Yet like clouds, it stops for no one♪

303
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:06,470
♪Put away those dreamlike words♪

304
00:15:06,470 --> 00:15:11,010
♪And forget at world's end♪

305
00:15:11,310 --> 00:15:12,810
♪Embracing memory♪

306
00:15:12,810 --> 00:15:15,180
♪Through blossoms and dreams♪

307
00:15:15,180 --> 00:15:19,060
♪You hide in the crowd, silent♪

308
00:15:19,060 --> 00:15:21,390
♪I wish to let it pass♪

309
00:15:21,390 --> 00:15:26,390
♪And run toward this vast life♪

